companyName: First Trust Morningstar Managed Futures Strategy Fund
description:
The investment seeks to achieve positive returns that uses as a benchmark, the Morningstar Diversified Futures Index.
 The fund is an actively managed exchange-traded fund that seeks to achieve positive returns that are not directly correlated to broad market equity or fixed income returns. It seeks to exceed the performance of the Benchmark by actively selecting investments for the fund with varying maturities from the underlying components of the Benchmark.
